object.script:
-- made by Toastery
fade_in_time = property.getNumber("Fade In (s)") ~= 0 and property.getNumber("Fade In (s)")*60 or 0.01 fade_out_time = property.getNumber("Fade Out (s)") ~= 0 and property.getNumber("Fade Out (s)")*60 or 0.01
init_values = { on = false, r = 0, g = 0, b = 0 }
last = init_values
start = init_values
tar = init_values
new = init_values
function onTick() cur = { on = input.getBool(1), r = input.getBool(1) and input.getNumber(1)/255 or 0, g = input.getBool(1) and input.getNumber(2)/255 or 0, b = input.getBool(1) and input.getNumber(3)/255 or 0 }
if tar.on ~= cur.on or tar.r ~= cur.r or tar.g ~= cur.g or tar.b ~= cur.b then tar = cur start = last end
if tar ~= last then
new = { on = cur.on, r = last.r < cur.r and math.clamp(last.r + (tar.r - start.r)/fade_in_time, 0, tar.r) or math.clamp(last.r + (tar.r - start.r)/fade_out_time, tar.r, 1), g = last.g < cur.g and math.clamp(last.g + (tar.g - start.g)/fade_in_time, 0, tar.g) or math.clamp(last.g + (tar.g - start.g)/fade_out_time, tar.g, 1), b = last.b < cur.b and math.clamp(last.b + (tar.b - start.b)/fade_in_time, 0, tar.b) or math.clamp(last.b + (tar.b - start.b)/fade_out_time, tar.b, 1), }
last = new end output.setBool(1, new.on) output.setNumber(1, new.r) output.setNumber(2, new.g) output.setNumber(3, new.b) end
function math.clamp(x, min, max) return max<x and max or min>x and min or x end

local delay = property.getNumber("Delay (s)")
delay = delay*60
local input_history = {}
for i = 1, delay do table.insert(input_history, 0) end
function onTick() local number_input = input.getNumber(1)
table.insert(input_history, number_input)
output.setNumber(1, input_history[1])
table.remove(input_history, 1) end

object.script:
-- Simple EPN, by Lassi#9944
lastRateX=0 lastRateY=0 lastAccX=0 lastAccY=0
navRate=property.getNumber("Rate nav") navAcc=property.getNumber("Acc nav") navJerk=property.getNumber("Jerk nav")
smoothclosingv=0
function onTick() rateX=input.getNumber(1) rateY=input.getNumber(2) closingv=-input.getNumber(3) distance=input.getNumber(4) guide=input.getBool(1) --smoothclosingv=smoothclosingv+(closingv-smoothclosingv)/2 smoothclosingv=closingv Tgo=math.min(distance/math.max(closingv*60,1),10)
accX=rateX-lastRateX accY=rateY-lastRateY jerkX=accX-lastAccX jerkY=accY-lastAccY
if accX==rateX then accX=0 end if accY==rateY then accY=0 end if jerkX==jerkX then jerkX=0 end if jerkY==jerkY then jerkY=0 end
if guide == true then output.setNumber(1,(rateX*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accX*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkX*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Yaw multiplier")) output.setNumber(2,(rateY*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accY*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkY*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Pitch multiplier")) end
output.setNumber(3,rateX) output.setNumber(4,rateY) output.setNumber(5,closingv) output.setNumber(6,smoothclosingv)
lastRateX=rateX lastRateY=rateY lastAccX=accX lastAccY=accY end

tab={} function onTick() value=input.getNumber(1) if value ~= 0 and math.abs(value) < 100 then table.insert(tab,value) end total=0 for i,v in ipairs(tab) do total=total+v end total=total/#tab if #tab>6 then table.remove(tab,1) end
if #tab==0 then total=0 end
output.setNumber(1, total) output.setNumber(2, input.getNumber(2)) end
